    <name>SigmaVault Desktop</name>
    <summary>Desktop interface for SigmaVault NAS OS</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
      SigmaVault Desktop is a modern GTK4 application for managing your SigmaVault NAS system. 
      It provides comprehensive monitoring and control over compression jobs, storage management, 
      agent swarm coordination, and system configuration.
        </p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Real-time dashboard with system metrics and compression statistics</li>
            <li>Compression job management with detailed progress tracking</li>
            <li>Storage management: disks, ZFS pools, datasets, and network shares</li>
            <li>Elite Agent Collective monitoring (40-agent swarm across 4 tiers)</li>
            <li>System settings: network configuration, service management, notifications</li>
            <li>Beautiful libadwaita interface with dark mode support</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
      Built with Python, GTK4, and libadwaita for a modern, responsive user experience.
        </p>
    </description>

    <launchable type="desktop-id">com.sigmavault.desktop.desktop</launchable>

